AngloGold Ashanti Says Worker Killed in Accident at Its Moab Khotsong Mine

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-18T07:48:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-18/anglogold-ashanti-says-worker-killed-in-accident-at-its-moab-khotsong-mine.html
AngloGold Ashanti Ltd. (ANG)  said a worker
was killed in an accident at its Moab Khotsong operation in
 South Africa  yesterday.  AngloGold commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
